source.name: Local Election Official 2008 Post Election Survey
source.description: FVAP post election survey of election administrator working in local election offices in all jurisdictions, including the District of Columbia and US territories, who are responsible for approving voter registration, assigning and sending out ballots to the voter, and accepting voted ballots.
